org.archive.wayback.replay.html

Interface StringTransformer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseHrefStringTransformer, BlockCSSStringTransformer, CompositeStringTransformer, ExtractInsertTransformer, IdentityStringTransformer, InlineCSSStringTransformer, JSStringTransformer, MetaRefreshUrlStringTransformer, MultiRegexReplaceStringTransformer, RegexReplaceStringTransformer, RewritingStringTransformer, URLStringTransformer

    public interface StringTransformer
    Transforms text with certain rewrite rules.

    Input text may be entire HTML, JavaScript block, or as small as single attribute value.
